The '''Eriadu Free HoloDaily''' was a [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] news agency based at [[Eriadu City/Legends|Eriadu City]]. It covered the [[Eriadu Trade Summit]]. [[Eru Matalis]] apparently worked for it at some point before the [[Stark Hyperspace War/Legends|Stark Hyperspace War]].

